        <mxCell id="f60_AicwPV8kYth9lWR6-75" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;spacingBottom=0;" value="&lt;sup&gt;1 &lt;/sup&gt;Deployment requests will reference a tag or commit SHA, not branch head, to ensure deterministic execution if branch changes between job issuance and job execution.&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;sup&gt;2 &lt;/sup&gt;Deployment requests will be configured such that they are claimed once and executed once. Re-runs will require human intervention.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;sup&gt;3 &lt;/sup&gt;Initial implementation will likely follow GitLab issues with labels; exact specification to follow in a future revision&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
